measurements.description: Three stately flowers on one upright, staked 35-cm inflorescence; dorsal sepal cupped, orange-pink, dark scarlet venation, spur 2.3-cm, orange-pink; lateral sepals broadly elliptic, orange-pink; petals cymbiform, orange-pink, overlaid yellow, spotted scarlet; lip narrowly lanceolate, reflexed apically, deep orange-pink, lighter basally; substance firm; texture velvet.
